These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, pomegranate, garlic, cabbage
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, australian, canadian, pakistani
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, townhouse, futuristic
1. the craftsman house is the person eating cabbage##1
2. the townhouse house is on the left of the australian##1
3. the person eating cabbage is in an odd position##4
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
5. the canadian is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
6. the futuristic house is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3
8. the futuristic house is between the pakistani and the person eating strawberry##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Food         | cabbage      | strawberry | pomegranate | garlic |
| Nationality   | canadian | turkish  | australian   | pakistani    |
| House     | craftsman     | townhouse    | futuristic    | gothic-revival      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, cabbage, pear, kiwi
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, d&b, classical, ambient
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, paramedic, librarian, scientist
1. the paramedic is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
2. the person eating kiwi is the fan of classical##1
3. the person eating pear is in an even position##4
4. the dancer is on the far right##1
5. the scientist is on the far left##1
6. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
7. the fan of r&b is between the person eating kiwi and the person eating cabbage##2
8. the fan of ambient is between the fan of d&b and the person eating pear##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Food         | kiwi | pear   | cabbage | peas  |
| Music-Genre   | classical     | r&b | ambient  | d&b |
| Job     | scientist        | librarian  | paramedic    | dancer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, traveling, dancing, photography
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, coffee, water, iced-tea
4 different pets are kept: pony, snake, rat, turtle
1. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is photography##2
2. the person drinking coffee is the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the pony is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
4. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking water is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person drinking juice##2
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Hobby          | card-games | traveling   | photography     | dancing     |
| Beverage   | coffee  | iced-tea | water   | juice  |
| Pet     | turtle      | snake | rat | pony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, brazilian, pakistani, american
House: cape-cod, cottage, modern, art-deco
4 different pets are kept: pony, goldfish, turtle, hamster
1. the art-deco house is in an even position##4
2. the brazilian is the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
4. the cottage house is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
5. the art-deco house is the owner of the pony##1
6. the pakistani is the cape-cod house##1
7. the modern house is the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Nationality   | japanese  | american   | pakistani     | brazilian |
| House   | modern  | art-deco      | cape-cod        | cottage     |
| Pet         | turtle | pony | hamster | goldfish   |

