.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, mystery, animation, disaster
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, tulip, daisy, begonia
House: ranch-style, palace, victorian, art-deco
1. the person watching disaster movies is the person who growsbegonia##1
2. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
3. the ranch-style house is the person who growsbegonia##1
4. the palace house is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
6. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1
7. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1
8. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
9. the person who growsrose is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary   | disaster   | animation | mystery |
| Flower         | tulip      | begonia | rose      | daisy |
| House     | palace | ranch-style        | art-deco       | victorian  |

