.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, january, april, july
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, basketball, badminton, sailing
City: hannover, paris, san-francisco, boston
1. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
7. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4
8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Birthday    | april   | july      | january       | may |
| Sport   | skiing | sailing | badminton     | basketball |
| City     | boston     | paris  | hannover | san-francisco |

