.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, doctor, security-guard, photographer
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, trike, tram, car
City: hannover, edinburgh, berlin, marseilles
1. the person traveling to berlin is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person driving the car and the person traveling to hannover##2
3. the person driving the car is the doctor##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the doctor##3
5. the musician is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the car is on the right of the photographer##1
7. the person driving the quad-bike is the musician##1
8. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Job      | security-guard   | photographer          | doctor | musician        |
| Transport   | tram     | trike | car   | quad-bike     |
| City           | hannover | edinburgh         | marseilles         | berlin |

