.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, lilac, chestnut, brown
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, may, december, february
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, taxi, snowmobile, jet-ski
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
2. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who likes turquise##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the taxi is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who likes turquise##2
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
7. the person who likes turquise is in an even position##4
8. the person who likes turquise is between the person who likes lilac and the person who likes chestnut##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Color         | lilac | turquise      | chestnut       | brown    |
| Birthday           | may  | december  | february | april |
| Transport   | jet-ski      | snowmobile | taxi         | bike    |

