.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, january, december, july
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, aconite, rose, iris
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, purple, fuchsia, chestnut
1. the person who growsmarigold is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
4. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
6. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
7. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
8. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
9. the person who growsiris is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Birthday   | january         | may  | december     | july         |
| Flower        | iris | aconite | marigold | rose         |
| Color      | purple         | fuchsia  | lavender   | chestnut |

