.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, coach, accountant, bartender
City: rome, san-francisco, venice, edinburgh
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, daisy, poppy, lily
 1. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the accountant##3
 2. the person traveling to rome is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the coach##1
 4. the person traveling to venice is between the coach and the librarian##2
 5. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the coach##3
 6. the person who growslily is the accountant##1
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far right##1
 8. the librarian is in an odd position##4
 9. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the bartender and the accountant##2
10. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Job   | librarian  | accountant    | coach | bartender    |
| City   | rome | venice | san-francisco  | edinburgh |
| Flower           | poppy   | lily    | marigold        | daisy   |

