.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, cooking, filmmaking, rock-climbing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, action, documentary, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, pony, goat, hedgehog
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
4. the person watching action movies is in an even position##4
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
7. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
9. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby      | drawing                | rock-climbing  | cooking | filmmaking   |
| Movie-Genre           | time-travel | action | animation   | documentary |
| Pet   | pony         | rabbit     | hedgehog     | goat |

