.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, swimming, lacrosse, surfing
House: victorian, art-deco, wooden, cottage
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, hot-chocolate, milk
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the art-deco house##1
5. the person drinking coffee is between the cottage house and the person drinking milk##2
6. the wooden house is in an even position##4
7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Sport          | lacrosse    | swimming  | surfing  | soccer |
| House   | cottage | art-deco | victorian | wooden |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate    | coffee     | milk    | soy-milk |

