.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, mystery, disaster, action
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, brown, black, yellow
House: futuristic, palace, ranch-style, art-deco
1. the palace house is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who likes apricot##2
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
4. the art-deco house is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
5. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
7. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
8. the person who likes black is the person watching time-travel movies##1
9. the person who likes yellow is between the ranch-style house and the futuristic house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre      | time-travel | disaster      | mystery  | action    |
| Color   | black   | brown | yellow | apricot |
| House           | art-deco      | ranch-style       | palace   | futuristic      |

