.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
4 different games are played: poker, billiard, canasta, go
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, bus, quad-bike, motorbike
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, ritmeester, aristoff, dannemann
1. the person playing canasta is in an even position##4
2. the person playing billiard is between the person playing go and the bolivar-smoker##2
3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person playing go is in an even position##4
5. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is between the bolivar-smoker and the person driving the snowmobile##2
7. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
9. the bolivar-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Game         | poker    | canasta | billiard  | go  |
| Transport   | quad-bike | bus       | motorbike | snowmobile |
| Cigar         | aristoff   | bolivar      | dannemann | ritmeester       |

