.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, january, april, august
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, peach, watermelon, tomato
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, tram, scooter, motorbike
1. the person driving the tram is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the tram is the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person eating peach##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is the person eating tomato##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
6. the person eating nectarine is the person driving the tram##1
7. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
8. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Birthday      | april      | january | december     | august    |
| Food   | tomato | nectarine      | peach | watermelon |
| Transport           | scooter   | tram  | airplane     | motorbike |

