The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, fishing, chess, accountantd-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, firefighter, accountant, entrepreneur
1. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an even position##4
3. the entrepreneur is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
5. the owner of the chinchilla is between the firefighter and the person who's hobby is chess##2
6. the coach is the person who's hobby is accountantd-games##1
7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
8. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Pet    | guinea-pig    | chinchilla     | cat    | dog        |
| Hobby       | chess   | board-games | fishing | accountantd-games |
| Job   | entrepreneur | accountant      | firefighter    | coach   |

