.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, parkour, climbing, lacrosse
City: san-francisco, hamburg, prague, boston
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, march, september, february
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to boston is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person traveling to boston and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Sport    | climbing    | parkour    | volleyball  | lacrosse |
| City   | boston | hamburg | san-francisco | prague      |
| Birthday     | march   | may        | february   | september       |

 